<head>
    <title>Bootstrap 4 Example</title>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.4.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.16.0/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>

    <style>
        .container {
            background-color: chocolate;
            height: 200px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        
        .container-fluid {
            background-color: chocolate;
            height: 200px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
    </style>

</head>

<body>
    <ol>
        <li>The <code>.container</code> class provides a responsive <strong>fixed width container</strong></li>
        <li>The <code>.container-fluid</code> class provides a <strong>full width container</strong>, spanning the entire width of the viewport</li>
    </ol>


    <div class="">

        <p>container</p>
    </div>

    <div class="">

        <p>container-fluid</p>
    </div>
